'''硅酸铪'''是[[铪|铪]]的[[硅酸|硅酸]][[盐|盐]]，[[化学式|化学式]]HfSiO<sub>4</sub>。

在现代半导体元件中，可以使用由[[原子层沉积|原子层沉积]]、[[化学气相沉积|化学气相沉积]]或[[有机金属化学气相沉积法|MOCVD]]生长的硅酸铪和[[硅酸锆|硅酸锆]][[薄膜|薄膜]]，作为[[高κ电介质|高κ电介质]]替换[[二氧化钛|二氧化钛]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Mitrovic|first1=I.Z.|last2=Buiu|first2=O.|last3=Hall|first3=S.|last4=Bungey|first4=C.|last5=Wagner|first5=T.|last6=Davey|first6=W.|last7=Lu|first7=Y.|title=Electrical and structural properties of hafnium silicate thin films|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0026271407000741|journal=Microelectronics Reliability|date=April 2007|volume=47|issue=4-5|pages=645–648|doi=10.1016/j.microrel.2007.01.065|access-date=2015-04-11|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924155023/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0026271407000741|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[二氧化铪|二氧化铪]]中的[[硅|硅]]增大了[[能隙|能隙]]，同时降低[[相对电容率|相对电容率]]。此外，它还提高了非晶膜的结晶化温度，并进一步增强了材料在高温下与硅的热稳定性<ref>{{cite journal |author=J.H. Choi et al. |year=2011 |journal=Materials Science and Engineering: R |title=Development of hafnium based high-k materials—A review |url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0927796X10001683 |publisher= |volume=72 |issue=6 |pages=97–136 |doi=10.1016/j.mser.2010.12.001 |pmc= |pmid= |access-date=2015-04-11 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924181532/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0927796X10001683 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有时会向硅酸铪中加入[[氮|氮]]以提高热稳定性和设备的电性能。

